OPTIGA Trust M Software framework
#################################

Origin:
   https://github.com/Infineon/optiga-trust-m

Status:
   8618e922d48f08f7e3fb11c854b1d0e22021fdb1

Import instructions:
   When we import optiga-trust-m we remove the examples/ dir and not nedded pal/ subdirs to reduce
   the amount of code imported.

Purpose:
   Framework that allows to interact with Infineon's OPTIGA Trust M secure elements.

Description:
This repository contains a target-agnostic Software Framework to make use of the OPTIGA™ Trust M security chip. 
The OPTIGA™ Trust M is a security solution based on a secure microcontroller.
Each device is shipped with a unique elliptic-curve keypair and a corresponding X.509 certificate.

This framework provides the core library to communicate and utilize the OPTIGA™ Trust M.

